                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-597542514" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-597542514" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="597542514">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/">tradition</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-02-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">后面几篇对明史研究总结还行</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="623433960">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-623433960" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-623433960" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="623433960">有用</a>
                </span>
